 we consider the problem of\nrevenue maximization for a risk neutral seller in presence of risk averse\nbuyers, and give a poly-time algorithm to design an optimal mechanism for the\nseller.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Jul 2011 04:38:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2011 22:41:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Jun 2012 04:04:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-28"}
