es on tabling with answer subsumption and consists of a transformation\nalong with an API for library functions that interface with answer subsumption.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Jul 2011 11:22:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-07-26"}
